- **UTM Parameter Tracking**: Comprehensive marketing attribution (campaign, content, medium, source, term)
- **Channel Classifiers**: Sequential rules for marketing channel attribution
- **Out-of-the-box Marketing Analytics**: Pre-built views for traffic, ad performance, and conversion tracking

### Enterprise Features
- **Single Sign-on**: Enterprise authentication integration
